
1. To use Min_Value & Max_value Number Properties:

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <title>JavaScript Number Application</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h3>JavaScript Arrays Application</h3>
        <script language="javascript" type="text/javascript">
           var maxVar = Number.MAX_VALUE;
            document.write("Maximum Value: " + maxVar + "<br>");
           var minVar = Number.MIN_VALUE;
            document.write("Minimum Value: " + minVar);
        </script>
    </body>
</html>

2. To use toExponential method:

             <script >
             var myNum = new Number(44.5);
             var myVar = myNum.toExponential();
             document.write("The toExponential: " + myVar);
             </script>

3. To use toString method:

 <script language="javascript" type="text/javascript">
           var myNum = new Number(44.5);
            document.write("The toString: " + myNum.toString(2));
        </script>
